{"type":"message","id":"8505dadd","parentId":"c1126845","timestamp":"2026-04-28T02:04:42.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gmail: No new emails in the last hour.\niCloud: 4 emails but they appear to all be from today or older - let me check the timestamps. The most recent is ID 9 from 2026-04-27 19:06+00:00 which is about 7 hours ago. Since the check is \"newer_than:1h\", I need to determine which ones arrived in the last hour.\n\nFor iCloud, I don't have a \"newer_than\" filter, so I'll need to compare timestamps. The current time is 2026-04-28 02:04 UTC. So 1 hour ago would be 2026-04-28 01:04 UTC.\n\n\nLooking at the iCloud emails more carefully, none of them arrived within the last hour - the most recent one came in at 19:06 UTC, about 7 hours ago. So for the last hour, I have no new emails in either Gmail or iCloud.\n","thinkingSignature":"141151f23458904ef3242dfe22ca88c7dd3d533dea685b2772a7c6cdb6fd31ab"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fgvzqr0z4t13_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","message":"📬 GMAIL — No new emails","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":321,"output":270,"cacheRead":19712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20303,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777341869786,"responseId":"063f48aeee6fb4a1028b32fd662ef3b0"}}
