{"type":"message","id":"19b41def","parentId":"90715d81","timestamp":"2026-04-28T02:04:59.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The iCloud emails are all from RC Leasing about the apartment application. They all relate to the same thread - waiting for Logan to complete his portion of the application. Let me classify them.\n\nActually, looking at the flags - message 8 has \"!\" and \"R\" flags, message 7 has just \"R\", and message 6 has \"R\". Message 9 has no flags. \"!\" typically means flagged/important, \"R\" means read.\n\nThese are all LOW PRIORITY since they're about an ongoing apartment application - they're not bills or urgent matters. They're more \"IMPORTANT\" personal correspondence but not urgent action needed.\n\nHowever, since the user is actively waiting for Logan to complete his application, I'll classify these as IMPORTANT since they're personal/apartment related.\n\n\nSo I'm looking at the inbox state - there are 4 messages total, but they appear to be from different dates, which suggests this might be an archive rather than the actual inbox. I need to clarify whether these are all inbox messages or if some have been moved.\n\nLooking at the timestamps more carefully, the envelope list shows dates ranging from January to April 2026, but none of them are from today, April 27th. Since the cron job is set to check for emails from the last hour (newer_than:1h), I should verify whether these messages actually meet that criteria or if I'm misunderstanding how himalaya filters the results.\n\nThe list command without date filtering could be showing the entire mailbox structure, not just recent messages. Since the cron job specifically asks for new emails and these all appear to be older, I'll report that there are no new iCloud emails for this check cycle, though I should note that messages from RC Leasing about the apartment application do exist in the mailbox.","thinkingSignature":"8219b900ce79c40191b0c464d4f78d5aa21d3779d5134a2c90d567f2f450562c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_edrkh90bqp2w_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","message":"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails (last 1h)\n\n📋 Recent thread in mailbox — RC Leasing (apartment inquiry):\n• RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment (Apr 27, 7:06 PM)\n  └ Amy says she may have a unit for your timeframe — reminds that Logan needs to complete his application first","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1389,"output":490,"cacheRead":20128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22007,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777341890110,"responseId":"063f48c2c5e660a009a3ffe94974986b"}}
